									<h1 class="title">The Ideas We'll Be Talking About in 2017</h1>
									<p class="meta"><time class="time" datetime="2017-07-27" itemprop="datePublished">27 Juli 2017</time> | By <a href="#" class="author">Distri Admin</a></p>
